id=mcpe_vv
name=Minecraft Vibrant Visuals Unlock
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=waydroid-nvidia
description=Detects the GPU at boot and patches Minecraft Bedrock's tiers.bin in place so Vibrant Visuals is selectable on any device (incl. Waydroid/Venus, emulators, unsupported phones). Re-applies automatically after Minecraft updates. No re-sign, no reinstall.
